{
  "message": "feat: add React Query infrastructure with localStorage persistence\n\nIntegrate TanStack Query (React Query v5) with localStorage persistence\nfor improved state management and offline-capable wizard flow.\n\nNew component: QueryProvider (apps/web/components/query-provider.tsx)\n- Creates QueryClient with persistence-optimized settings:\n  - staleTime: Infinity (data never goes stale automatically)\n  - gcTime: Infinity (cache never garbage collected)\n  - refetchOnWindowFocus: false (no refetch on tab switch)\n  - refetchOnReconnect: false (no refetch on network restore)\n  - retry: false (no automatic retries for localStorage data)\n- Uses createSyncStoragePersister for localStorage persistence\n- Storage key: \"acfs-query-cache\"\n- SSR-safe: Falls back to regular QueryClientProvider during SSR\n- Uses PersistQueryClientProvider on client for automatic\n  cache hydration and persistence\n\nRoot layout integration (apps/web/app/layout.tsx):\n- Import QueryProvider component\n- Wrap existing provider tree with QueryProvider\n- Maintains existing nesting: Query > Motion > Analytics > children\n- All providers remain within Suspense boundary\n\nNew dependencies (apps/web/package.json):\n- @tanstack/react-query (^5.90.12): Core query library\n- @tanstack/react-query-persist-client (^5.90.14): Persistence adapter\n- @tanstack/query-sync-storage-persister (^5.90.14): localStorage sync\n- @tanstack/react-form (^1.27.5): Form state management\n- @tanstack/zod-form-adapter (^0.42.1): Zod schema integration\n\nThis infrastructure enables future wizard improvements:\n- Persist wizard progress across page refreshes\n- Cache VPS provider data for offline access\n- Share state between wizard steps without prop drilling\n- Type-safe form handling with Zod validation\n\n\ud83e\udd16 Generated with [Claude Code](https://claude.com/claude-code)\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
